text: 131. Terima kasih. #Diplomacy4PeaceandProsperity #Diplomacy4You #PPTM2020

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: 118.  Tahun ini, Indonesia akan membuka perwakilan di Younde, Kamerun dan meningkatkan status Kepala Perwakilan RI di Antananarivo dari Kuasa Tetap menjadi Duta Besar.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: 117.  Beban tugas rangkapan dan hal-hal terkait Perwakilan RI di luar negeri akan terus ditinjau ulang sesuai kebutuhan.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: 116. Kementerian Luar Negeri telah menghapus jabatan eselon IV sejak tahun 2017 dan dalam waktu dekat jabatan eselon III sebagian besar akan dihapus digantikan penguatan jabatan fungsional.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: 115. Prioritas terakhir adalah pembangunan infrastruktur diplomasi. Dalam 5 tahun terakhir banyak infrastruktur diplomasi telah dibangun. Kementerian Luar Negeri dan Perwakilan RI di luar negeri akan terus melakukan reformasi dan efisiensi.

text: 85. Indonesia akan terus melawan terhadap negara asing yg secara jelas-jelas memberikan dukungan terhadap gerakan separatisme di Indonesia, karena ini jelas pelanggaran terhadap hukum internasional dan prinsip Piagam PBB. #Diplomacy4You

text: 53.       Rivalitas penting untuk diubah menjadi kerja sama. Trust deficit harus diganti menjadi strategic trust #Diplomacy4PeaceandProsperity

text: Ziyaret sirasinda, 12-16 yaslari arasinda 17 genç dansçidan olusan bu dans grubu, birkaç ögretmen ve organize eden komitesinin temsilcisi Saim Oguz Beyefendi ile geldiler. Bazi dans grubu temsilcileri, olaylardan edindikleri deneyimlerini ve heyecanlarini paylastilar.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Türkiye Egitim Kurumu tarafindan davet edilmis ve 2 farkli sehrinde (Atasehir 22 -24/04/2018) ve Ankara (25-27/04/2018) dans gösterisi yapilmisti. Saman & Bali dansi gösterdikten sonra seyirciden yüksek sesle alkis aldi ve "En Iyi Dans Performanslari" ödülüne almislar.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: 26 Nisan 2018'de Türkiye için Endonezya Büyükelçisi, Ankara'da bulunan Diplomatik Residanz´ta Kinnarii Promosindo Dans Grubu - SMP N 85 Jakarta'nin ziyaretini karsiladi. SMP N 85 Jakarta'nin dans grubu 23 Nisan 2018'de TC Ulusal Çocuk Bayrami kutlamalarina katildi.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: The Indonesian Ambassador for Turkey also expressed his appreciation to Kinnarii Promosindo Dance Group – SMP N 85 Jakarta who has participated in the name of the nation and promoted Indonesian culture to Turkey.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: During the visit, the group consisting of 17 teen dancers aged 12-16 years, was accompanied by several teachers and Mr. Saim Oguz as representative of the organizing committee. Some of the dance group representatives shared their experiences&excitement they got from the event.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: They´re invited by the local education department to perform dances to celebrate in two different cities in Turkey, Istanbul (Atasehir 22-24/04/2018) and Ankara (25-27/04/2018). Bringing Saman & Bali dances, the group was awarded the "Best Dance Performances" award.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: On 26 April 2018, the Indonesian Ambassador for Turkey warmly welcomed the visit of Kinnarii Promosindo Dance Group-SMPN 85 Jakarta at Wisma Duta Ankara. The dance group from SMP N 85 Jakarta participated in the celebration of the National Children's Day of Turkey 23 April 2018.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Dubes RI turut menyampaikan apresiasinya terhadap grup Gaya Tari Kinnarii Promosindo – SMPN 85 Jakarta yang telah ikut mengharumkan nama bangsa dan mempromosikan budaya Indonesia hingga ke Turki.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Beberapa anak-anak perwakilan grup tari tersebut menceritakan pengalaman dan keseruan yang didapat dari rangkaian acara tersebut.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Dalam kunjungannya, grup yang berjumlah 17 penari remaja berusia 12-16 tahun ini hadir dengan didampingi oleh beberapa guru dan Mr. Saim Oguz sebagai perwakilan panitia penyelenggara acara.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Membawakan tari saman dan tari bali, grup Gaya Tari Kinnarii Promosindo – SMPN 85 Jakarta mendapat sambutan yang meriah dari penonton dan mendapatkan penghargaan “Best Dance Performances”.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Grup tari yang berasal dari SMP N 85 Jakarta ini turut berpartisipasi dalam peringatan Hari Anak Nasional Turki yang jatuh pada tanggal 23 April 2018 lalu. Mereka diundang oleh dinas pendidikan setempat untuk memeriahkan peringatan tersebut di 2 kota berbeda di Turki.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Pada tanggal 26 April 2018, Dubes RI menyambut dengan hangat kunjungan yang dilakukan grup Gaya Tari Kinnarii Promosindo – SMP N 85 Jakarta di Wisma Duta Ankara. https://t.co/L5SayT9JBt

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Ardindan 14 Nisan 2018'de Ankara Büyükelçiligi, Samsun'daki Endonezyalilarla da bir iliski ve diyalog yürüttü. Samsun'da toplam 55 kisi Endonezyali katildi.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Ayrica Büyükelçi, Trabzon'daki Endonezyalilarla bir toplanti ve diyalog düzenledi. Trabzon ve çevre bölgelerde (Giresun, Rize, ve Erzurum) ögrenim gören ögrenciler ve ögrencilerden olusan 40 kisi Endonezyali vatandaslari bulunun.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Turkiye icin Endonezya Büyükelçisi, 13 Nisan 2018 tarihinde Trabzon'daki Endonezya vatandaslariyla ilgili çesitli konularin ele alinmasinda isbirligini güçlendirmek amaciyla Trabzon Il Emniyet Müdürü Orhan Çevik ile bir araya geldi.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Then, on April 14, 2018 and then, the Embassy of Ankara has also conducted a relationship and dialogue with the Indonesian people in Samsun. A total of 55 Indonesians in Samsun who are mostly students and santri attended the occasion.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: In addition, the Ambassador held a meeting and dialogue with the Indonesian people in Trabzon. Present on the occasion as many as 40 Indonesian citizens who mostly consists of students and students who are studying in Trabzon and surrounding areas (Giresun, Rize, Erzurum).

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Indonesian Ambassador for Turkey has met with Trabzon Provincial Police Chief Orhan Cevik in order to strengthen cooperation in handling various issues that arise related to the existence of Indonesian society in Trabzon on 13 April 2018.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Kemudian, pada 14 April 2018 lalu, KBRI Ankara pun telah melakukan silaturahmi & dialog dengan masyarakat Indonesia di Samsun. Sebanyak 55 orang WNI di Samsun yang mayoritas terdiri atas pelajar dan santri hadir dalam kesempatan tersebut.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Disamping itu, Dubes RI mengadakan pertemuan & dialog dengan masyarakat Indonesia di Trabzon. Hadir dalam kesempatan tersebut sebanyak 40 orang WNI yang mayoritas terdiri atas mahasiswa/i&santri yang sedang menempuh pendidikannya di Trabzon & sekitarnya (Giresun, Rize, Erzurum).

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Dubes RI Wardana telah melakukan pertemuan dengan Kepala Polisi Provinsi Trabzon Orhan Cevik dalam rangka memperkuat kerjasama dalam penaganan berbagai permasalahan yang muncul terkait keberadaan masyarakat Indonesia di Trabzon pada 13 April 2018 lalu. https://t.co/KlfpNnHxXb

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Diyanet Baskani ayrica, Endonezya'daki ögrencilerin çesitli dini egitim kurumlarinda ögrenim görmeleri için burs vermeye hazir olduklarini ifade etti.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: The President of Diyanet also expressed his readiness to provide scholarships for Indonesian students to study at various religious education institutions in Turkey.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Presiden Diyanet pun menyatakan kesiapannya untuk memberikan beasiswa bagi pelajar/mahasiswa Indonesia untuk belajar di berbagai lembaga pendidikan keagamaan di Turki.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Bu vesileyle, iki ülke arasinda isbirligini gelistirmeye yönelik çabalar konusunda fikir alisverisinde bulunuldu, mesela Islam Rahmatan Lil Alamin hakkinda konusma yapti ve din alaninda egitim isbirliginin gelistirilmesi.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: On the occasion, there has been an exchange of ideas on efforts to improve cooperation between the two countries, such as promoting Islam Rahmatan Lil Alamin and the development of educational cooperation in the field of religion.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: Dalam kesempatan tersebut telah dilakukan tukar pikiran tentang upaya meningkatkan kerjasama kedua negara, antara lain mempromosikan Islam Rahmatan Lil Alamin serta pengembangan kerjasama pendidikan dibidang agama.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
text: 11 Nisan 2018'de Turkiye icin Endonezya Büyükelçisi, Diyanet Isleri Baskanligi'nin (Türkiye Yüksek Diyanet Isleri Kurumu) yeni Baskani Prof. Dr. Ali Erbas.

name: Indonesian Embassy Ankara
